{"tid":651162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】美軍基地禁售華為中興手機 美擬限制中國電訊公司發展","createTime":"2018-05-03T01:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T02:15:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f499365925b6f70673de88374862eef9920948f0","tid":651162,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:37:19.000Z","msg":"美中貿易談判在北京登場前夕，《華爾街日報》報道，特朗普政府考慮以國安為由，用行政措施限制中國商華為、商中興通訊等中國廠商在美銷售電訊設備的能力，此舉恐引發北京報復。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部上月以違反制裁措施為由，禁止美國廠商向中興供應關鍵零組件7年。華為亦據傳遭美國司法部調查是否違反美方制裁伊朗的規定。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述多名消息人士報道，白宮未來幾周可能發佈行政命令，對與美國政府有商業往來的企業設限，要求這些企業使用的網路設備不得由「可能構成國安風險」的廠商製造。<br />\n美國國防部官員本周表示，他們正著手禁止全球各地美軍基地售販華為與中興的手機。美方官員擔心，北京可能命令電訊商入侵旗下產品進行監控，或是擾亂、切斷通訊。即使華為與中興已多次強調這種情況絕不會發生，美國與諸多盟友近期仍加強審查中國廠商設備在網路中的使用情形。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，白宮一旦發出行政命令，將代表美中在科技與電訊領域的鬥爭顯著升級。<br />\n<br />\n美方官員曾考慮是否要採取安全測試，過濾部份可疑的設備。但此舉可能引發新的問題，行政命令牽連範圍多廣也是未知數，美方因此尚未做出最後決定。<br />\n<br />\n美中在科技與電信領域角力，只是兩國貿易摩擦的一部分。為緩和貿易爭端，美國財長姆努欽（Steven Mnuchin）率團，今明兩天到北京和中國國務院副總理劉鶴領軍的代表團舉行會談，試圖縮小貿易逆差。<br />\n美中正處於開發新一代行動通訊技術的競賽，美方極力阻擋中國開發能在全球通用的5G行動網路，執全球電訊設備牛耳的華為因此被視為眼中釘。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部已揚言，假使美國企圖遏制中國發展，迫使中國讓步，中方捍衞利益的決心絲毫不會動搖，「會進行堅決的鬥爭」。<br />\n<br />\n美國半導體大廠高通（Qualcomm）便遭受池魚之殃。高通為在智慧型手機市場飽和之際讓產品多元化，併購荷蘭車用晶片廠商恩智浦半導體（NXP Semiconductors），但在北京技術性阻撓下，這宗交易面臨阻滯。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180503/58146178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58146178&d=iTNeUyVBVo3%2B%2BTLVzYBApTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=8f0019b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58146178&h=c6deb18b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180503/58146178</a>"},{"pid":"bd7c6799e011447c9a90255aeebe3073e1fa6a2d","tid":651162,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"科研又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火燭又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中興又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美興又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵制又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔抵制都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750cd90ebe8e9e4514b22abf532e1826da291c80","tid":651162,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/094032_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F094032_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png&h=631e1eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/094038_8169b091ed9a14f173810906701f5ab8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F094038_8169b091ed9a14f173810906701f5ab8.jpg&h=2d6a0ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"daaefc89d0e27b0cccba4dbc095cb8f49b536c3c","tid":651162,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國半導體大廠高通（Qualcomm）便遭受池魚之殃。高通為在智慧型手機市場飽和之際讓產品多元化，併購荷蘭車用晶片廠商恩智浦半導體（NXP Semiconductors），<span style=\"color: red;\">但在北京技術性阻撓下</span>，這宗交易面臨阻滯。</blockquote><br />\n求解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3c998f1735fea0dc3ab3bd053c00718ae753e3","tid":651162,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國商務部已揚言，假使美國企圖遏制中國發展，迫使中國讓步，中方捍衞利益的決心絲毫不會動搖，「會進行堅決的鬥爭」。</span><br />\n<br />\n贏呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}